        <h2 class="basics__slogan">Feed your cooking addiction and Neighbors</h2>
        <p class="basics__description">Fuel your baking or cooking addiction and get acquainted with your neighbors at the same time through Pass the Bread Basket. An app that allows neighbors in your building to call dibs on a serving of a homemade good.</p>
        <div class="basics__buttonContainer">
            <button class="default basics__buildingButton"><a href="/buildings/">Find Your Building</a></button>
